      "date": "2013-01-16 11:08:43.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/994a597e-5fc9-11e2-84d4-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
